title: The Rochester Area Vegan Society
description: RAVS is a non-profit, non-sectarian educational organization that strives to provide: educational resources for informing the public about the advantages of a vegetarian life-style, nutritional information that will support and facilitate the adoption and healthful enjoyment of a vegetarian diet, insight into the impact of animal-centered diets on human health, on the integrity of our environment, on world hunger, and on cruelty needlessly inflicted on billions of living, feeling, creatures every year.
